                </ul>The above activities resulted in significantly improved public service delivery, safety and quality of life in San Antonio.<p><br></p>
                <p><strong>Business Tools Customized to Boost Public Agency Performance</strong><br>Process improvement activities related to business process analysis and redesign including risk and issue mitigation for contracted functions and operations have been developed and implemented with success in the State of Texas agencies, Special Districts (Port Authority of Houston and Port Authority of New York and New Jersey) and local public agencies such as the City of San Antonio using Total Quality Management approaches, Service Level Agreement development and Management by Objective approaches.</p>
                <p>Evaluation metrics to determine if programs are achieving results on an ongoing basis are a critical service Wendorf Beward &amp; Partners has performed. Most recently Wendorf Beward & Partners has assisted the Port Authority of Houston in the development of Service Level Agreements and other performance measurement tools in regards to a Strategic Asset Management Program.</p>
